i  went for dinner there last night..... i had the selection of oyster and went fo the  steak frites. that was soooo yummy!!!!! ii actually don't think i have had better steak for quite a while now... plus they have a huge list of wine including the chateau-neuf 05...amazing!!!! the hosts were all beautiful and gracious, very helpful, my waitress incredibly helpful and quick on her feet. expect to see more of me Great food, great service, in love!
